üéØ ADDITIONAL IMPORTANT CONCEPTS YOU SHOULD KNOW

‚úÖ FINAL EASY 5-POINT SUMMARY (CRYSTAL CLEAR)

Static block ‚Üí runs once when class loads
Instance block ‚Üí runs for every object before constructor
Static variable ‚Üí stored in method area, long life, default values
Instance variable ‚Üí stored in heap, dies with object
Local/parameter variables ‚Üí stored in stack, no default value, shortest life

