| Var Type                    | Declared         | Memory      | Scope             | Access              | Modifiers                                | Lifetime               |
| --------------------------- | ---------------- | ----------- | ----------------- | ------------------- | ---------------------------------------- | ---------------------- |
| **Static (Class Variable)** | Inside class     | Method Area | Entire program    | Class name / object | All except abstract/sync/native/strictfp | Till JVM ends          |
| **Instance Variable**       | Inside class     | Heap        | Per object        | Object ref          | All except abstract/sync/native/strictfp | Until object destroyed |
| **Local Variable**          | Inside method    | Stack       | Method/block only | Inside same block   | Only final                               | Until method ends      |
| **Parameter Variable**      | Method signature | Stack       | Method only       | Inside method       | Only final                               | Until method ends      |

